{"word":"G4416 - πρωτότοκος - prōtótokos - pro-tot-ok'-os - Firstbegotten","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρωτότοκος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prōtótokos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-tot-ok'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Firstbegotten</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முதற்பேறான, முதற்பிறந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"firstborn"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4413 - πρῶτος - prōtos - pro'-tos/4413\">G4413</a> and the alternate of <a href=\"#/G5088 - τίκτω - tíktō - tik'-to/5088\">G5088</a>; <i>first born</i> (usually as noun, literally or figuratively): - firstbegotten (-born).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4409/4409\">G4409</a>, <a href=\"#/G4410/4410\">G4410</a>, <a href=\"#/G4411/4411\">G4411</a>, <a href=\"#/G4412/4412\">G4412</a>, <a href=\"#/G4413/4413\">G4413</a>, <a href=\"#/G4414/4414\">G4414</a>, <a href=\"#/G4415/4415\">G4415</a>, <a href=\"#/G4416/4416\">G4416</a>"}]}